  <section class="border-t border-stone-200/60 bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">Preguntas Frecuentes sobre Terrenos en Coyhaique</h2>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Cuánto cuesta una terreno en Coyhaique?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Los precios de terrenos en Coyhaique van desde UF 1,64 hasta UF 205, con un promedio de UF NaN. Los precios varían según ubicación, tamaño y estado. La UF (Unidad de Fomento) es la unidad de cuenta reajustable utilizada en transacciones inmobiliarias en Chile.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Es buen momento para comprar terrenos en Coyhaique?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">El mercado inmobiliario en Coyhaique ha mostrado un crecimiento sostenido de aproximadamente 10-15% anual en los últimos cinco años. La Patagonia sigue atrayendo compradores que buscan naturaleza, calidad de vida y potencial de inversión.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Qué requisitos hay para comprar terreno en Coyhaique?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Tanto ciudadanos chilenos como extranjeros pueden comprar propiedades en Coyhaique. El proceso incluye: (1) firmar una promesa de compraventa, (2) realizar el estudio de títulos en el Conservador de Bienes Raíces, (3) firmar la escritura ante notario, y (4) inscribir la transferencia. El financiamiento está disponible a través de bancos chilenos mediante crédito hipotecario en UF, con tasas del 3,5-5,5% anual y hasta 80% de financiamiento.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Cómo es vivir en Coyhaique?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Capital regional con los servicios más completos de Aysén. Centro financiero, administrativo y de conectividad aérea de la Patagonia chilena. Veranos de hasta 20°C e inviernos que bajan a -3°C, con aproximadamente 1100mm de precipitación anual.</p></details>
      <details class="mt-4 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 group"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 text-left font-semibold text-stone-900 marker:[content:''] after:ml-4 after:inline-block after:size-5 after:shrink-0 after:bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2024%2024%22%20stroke-width%3D%222%22%20stroke%3D%22currentColor%22%3E%3Cpath%20stroke-linecap%3D%22round%22%20stroke-linejoin%3D%22round%22%20d%3D%22m19%209-6%206%206-6-6%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E')] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-center after:transition-transform after:group-open:rotate-180">¿Qué servicios hay en Coyhaique?</summary><p class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">Coyhaique cuenta con Hospital Regional, Universidad, Aeropuerto Balmaceda (55 km), Supermercados, Bancos. La Región de Aysén continúa mejorando su infraestructura con mejores conexiones viales y servicios ampliados.</p></details>
